{"article_id":"k6otycdagJtcjFod","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON-President Trump said Thursday","depth":8},{"id":1,"text":"that the White House and congressional negotiators were no closer to an immigration deal ,","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"five days after he agreed to end the partial government shutdown ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"and reiterated","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"he is willing to act alone","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"to build a wall on the southern border .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"\" I ' m not waiting for this committee , \"","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"Mr. Trump said ,","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"referring to a bipartisan group of legislators from the House and Senate","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"who are working to hash out an agreement","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that would prevent another shutdown Feb 15 .","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"Asked if he was closer or further from a deal","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"since he agreed to end the shutdown on Jan. 25 ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"he \" would say","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"we ' re the same. \"","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"the biggest barrier was Democrats","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"who oppose the wall .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"House Speaker Nancy Pelosi","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"( D. , Calif. ) ,","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"meanwhile , reiterated","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"that Democrats wouldn ' t support funding for a concrete border wall as part of the negotiations ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"but indicated some openness to other forms of physical barriers .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" There ' s not going to be any wall money in the legislation , \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Mrs. Pelosi told reporters .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"But she didn ' t rule out certain other physical barriers ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"citing \" Normandy fencing , \"","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"which has crisscrossed posts .","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"\" Is there a place","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"where enhanced fencing , Normandy fencing , would work ?","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"Let them have that discussion , \"","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"she said ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"referring to the bipartisan group of 17 lawmakers .","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"House Democratic leaders said this week","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"they could support \" enhanced fencing \"","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"where experts say","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"it is needed .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"\" If there ' s no wall ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"it doesn ' t work .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"She ' s just playing games , \"","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Mr. Trump said of Ms. Pelosi .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"He said","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"the House speaker would be \" begging for a wall \"","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"if an existing barricade was removed","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"that separated the Mexican border city of Tijuana from California , Mrs. Pelosi ' s home state .","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"\" She will say","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"' Mr . President ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"please , please give us a wall , ' \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"Meanwhile , senior Republicans on the group shrugged off Mr. Trump ' s comments in a tweet earlier Thursday","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"that they were \" wasting their time , \"","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"given his assertion","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"that Democrats wouldn ' t agree to wall funding .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"\" I haven ' t given up on that yet .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"I ' m not exuberant about it ,","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"but I ' m still hopeful , \"","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"Senate Appropriations Committee Chairman Richard Shelby","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"( R. , Ala. )","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"said about the group ' s prospects .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Mr. Trump said","depth":6},{"id":61,"text":"he wouldn ' t have done anything differently","depth":7},{"id":62,"text":"if Republicans hadn ' t lost the House majority in November elections .","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"Instead ,","depth":6},{"id":64,"text":"he said","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"the shutdown helped educate Americans to the need for a border wall .","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"\" We ' ve set the stage for what ' s going to happen , \"","depth":5},{"id":67,"text":"Mr. Trump said .","depth":5},{"id":68,"text":"Mr. Trump has considered acting on the wall","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"without Congress","depth":8},{"id":70,"text":"by declaring a national emergency","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"and using executive powers","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"to authorize spending money on construction .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"That plan would almost certainly face immediate challenges in court .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"The president said Thursday","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"he would wait until the self-imposed deadline of Feb. 15","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"to decide on whether to declare a national emergency .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"The revived prospect has stirred consternation in some right-leaning circles .","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"Some Republicans , such as Sen. Mike Lee of Utah , take a skeptical approach to the use of executive authority","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"and would be likely to demand specific statutory justifications for any action on the southern border .","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"The Federalist Society , the network of conservative lawyers","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"that has played a prominent role in Mr. Trump ' s nominations to the Supreme Court ,","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"hosted a debate Thursday about the issue ,","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"and the likelihood","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"such a declaration could set a precedent","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that could backfire for conservatives in the future .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"\" Would a future President Kamala Harris say","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"global warming is a national emergency ? \"","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"asked David French , a conservative commentator and one of the speakers in the debate ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"referring to the California senator","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"who is seeking the Democratic presidential nomination .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Another area of concern for some on the right is the prospect","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"of the Democratic-controlled House establishing more opportunities","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"to sue the administration over its use of executive power .","depth":9},{"id":94,"text":"Aides to lawmakers on the bipartisan committee are expected to meet Friday and over the weekend , with the goal","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"of cutting a deal next week .","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"Mr. Shelby said","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"Democrats ' comments","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"indicating a potential willingness","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"to fund physical barriers","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"left him \" hopeful . \"","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Mr. Shelby said","depth":8},{"id":102,"text":"it wasn ' t entirely clear to him what level of wall funding Mr. Trump would require","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"to sign off on the agreement .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"\" That ' s the central question here , \"","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"When asked why the president hadn ' t told him ,","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"Mr. Shelby said","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"\" maybe he hasn ' t decided yet . \"","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"House Democrats on Thursday morning released a proposal","depth":2},{"id":110,"text":"detailing how they would fund the entire Homeland Security Department ,","depth":3},{"id":111,"text":"which oversees the border .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":220,"right":222,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":220,"left":171,"right":219,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":171,"left":161,"right":170,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":161,"left":130,"right":160,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":122,"right":129,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":117,"right":121,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":114,"right":116,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":114,"left":0,"right":113,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":113,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":3,"right":115,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":115,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":118,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":8,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":129,"left":126,"right":128,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":123,"right":125,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":13,"right":124,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":128,"left":16,"right":127,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":127,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":160,"left":148,"right":159,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":144,"right":147,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":134,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearit